column1: Uchi////- Jar Jar Duck - as the most expensive dish on the menu
column2: the jar jar duck was quite disappointing.  Sealed within a jar
column3: the countryside farms duck is prepared two different ways--crispy and roasted--and paired with kumquat and endive and immersed in rosemary smoke.  The smoke penetrates the meat well
column4: but gives it a smoky flavor that doesn't complement the flavor of the duck.
